@startuml
!theme plain

actor User
participant "Popup/Options UI" as UI
participant "Background Script" as BS
participant "Content Script" as CS
database "Precomputed Words Database" as PWD
participant "TTS Module" as TTS

User -> UI : Adjusts Settings
UI -> BS : Updates Settings
BS -> CS : Applies Settings
CS -> PWD : Requests Transformations
PWD -> CS : Returns Variations
CS -> UI : Renders Transformed Text
CS --> TTS : Activates for Selected Text

@enduml
